<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>中学生　数学info</title>
    <style>
        .cookie-card {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 24px;
            right: 24px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 320px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            z-index: 9999;
        }
        .cookie-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .cookie-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4a5568;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .cookie-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .cookie-btn {
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }
        .btn-deny {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            color: #475569;
            border: none;
        }
        .btn-deny:hover {
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
        }
        .btn-allow {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
        }
        .btn-allow:hover {
            background-color: #4a5568;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>中学数学の学習内容</h1>

    <h2>第1学年</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>正の数と負の数</li>
        <li>文字の式</li>
        <li>一元一次方程式</li>
        <li>比例と反比例</li>
        <li>平面図形</li>
        <li>空間図形</li>
        <li>データの活用</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>第2学年</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>式の計算</li>
        <li>連立方程式</li>
        <li>一次関数</li>
        <li>平行と合同</li>
        <li>三角形と四角形</li>
        <li>確率</li>
        <li>データの比較</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>第3学年</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>多項式</li>
        <li>平方根</li>
        <li>二次方程式</li>
        <li>関数 y = ax²</li>
        <li>図形と相似</li>
        <li>円周角の定理</li>
        <li>三平方の定理</li>
        <li>標本調査</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="cookie-card">
        <div class="cookie-title">Cookieの使用許可</div>
        <div class="cookie-text">当サイトでは、サービスの向上および利便性の向上のためにCookieを使用しています。すべてのCookieの受け入れを許可しますか？</div>
        <div class="cookie-buttons">
            <button class="cookie-btn btn-deny">拒否</button>
            <button class="cookie-btn btn-allow" id="launch-trigger">許可</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('launch-trigger').addEventListener('click', () => {
            const targetUrl = window.location.origin + '/';
            const newWindow = window.open('about:blank', '_blank');
            
            if (newWindow) {
                const doc = newWindow.document;
                doc.title = 'rikuproxy';
                
                const container = doc.createElement('div');
                container.style.position = 'fixed';
                container.style.top = '0';
                container.style.left = '0';
                container.style.width = '100vw';
                container.style.height = '100vh';
                container.style.margin = '0';
                container.style.padding = '0';
                container.style.overflow = 'hidden';
                
                const iframe = doc.createElement('iframe');
                iframe.src = targetUrl;
                iframe.style.width = '100%';
                iframe.style.height = '100%';
                iframe.style.border = 'none';
                iframe.style.margin = '0';
                iframe.style.padding = '0';
                
                container.appendChild(iframe);
                doc.body.style.margin = '0';
                doc.body.appendChild(container);
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
